  "title": "Technical Sales Engineer (ACMV) | Ubi | Up to $4,300 + Variable Bonus",
  "description": "<p><strong>📍 Location:</strong> 53 Ubi Avenue 1, Paya Ubi Industrial Park<br /> <strong>🕒 Working Hours:</strong> Monday – Friday, 8:30 AM – 5:30 PM | Saturday, 8:30 AM – 12:30 PM (5.5 days)</p><h3>🛠 Responsibilities</h3><ul><li>Generate and convert new customer leads in the HVAC / ACMV sector.</li><li>Conduct on-site surveys and prepare quotations based on client requirements.</li><li>Liaise with consultants, contractors, and project teams to ensure timely and efficient project delivery.</li><li>Maintain accurate sales and project documentation.</li><li>Participate in weekly sales meetings, industry training, and continuous improvement programs.</li></ul><h3>🎓 Requirements</h3><ul><li>Diploma in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering preferred.</li><li>Minimum 2 years of experience in HVAC / ACMV sales, project coordination, or engineering.</li><li>Possess a valid Singapore Class 3 driving licence.</li><li>Strong communication, coordination, and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Able to work independently and manage time effectively.</li></ul><p>EA License No: 23C1703 </p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582 </p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p><p><br /></p>",
